ISLAMABAD, Jan 9 (APP): President Dr Arif Alvi Saturday telephoned Chairman Senate Sadiq Sanjrani and condoled with him over the death of his 19 year old younger brother who died in a car accident.
The President prayed Allah Almighty to rest the departed soul in eternal peace and grant courage to the bereaved family to bear the loss with fortitude.
